
Utility scripts used for sspl development purpose.

####################################################################
# encryptor.py
####################################################################
- This script is useful to encrypt or decrypt passwords
  used in sspl config
- Requirements
  - cortx-py-utils
- Usage
  - ./encryptor.py <encrypt|decrypt> <text> <cluster-id> <service-name>
  - Ex. encryptor.py encrypt foo 001 rabbitmq
  - Services being used in sspl
     - rabbitmq
     - storage_enclosure
